@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f2f7fc;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #4285f4;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <p>We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard the information you provide to us.</p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect your name, contact information, and demographic details when you use our website.</p>

        <h2>How We Use the Information</h2>
        <p>We use the collected information to better understand your needs, improve our products and services, and provide you with relevant updates and offers.</p>

        <h2>Security</h2>
        <p>We take appropriate measures to ensure the security of your information and prevent unauthorized access or disclosure.</p>

        <h2>Controlling Your Personal Information</h2>
        <p>You have the right to restrict the use of your personal information. We do not sell, distribute, or lease your information to third parties unless required by law.</p>

        <p>For more details about our privacy practices, please refer to our complete <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
    </div>

    
   
</body>
</html>
